a.n: Ms Nicolette's Academy For Exceptional Women

p.k: Ms Nicolette, the dean of an elite women's college, is willing to do anything to help her students succeed. Shay, a particularly petulant student, has spent the majority of the semester sending dirty texts to her boyfriend - spending so much time sexting has put a real strain on her GPA. Ms Nicolette knows the only way to get Shay back on track is to eradicate her hot, horny urges...and Ms Nicolette's just the woman for the job.
